    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are consistent with MRL 2 scoping. CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index satisfies RH < 1 acceptance criterion at all 5 evaluated operating points. The assessment team concludes the model has sufficient credibility to support the intended regulatory decision for the Class II CPB device submission.",
